swatchbooker (0.8-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Port to Python 3 and PySide6 (Qt6); drop Python 2 / PyQt4 / lcms 1.x
  * Migrate from lcms (1.x) to lcms2 (2.x)
  * Replace setup.py/setup.cfg with pyproject.toml (setuptools backend)
  * Update debian/control: require python3-pyside6, python3-pil, liblcms2-2
  * Update debian/rules: switch from cdbs+python-distutils to dh+pybuild
  * Bump debhelper compat level from 7 to 13
  * Update Standards-Version to 4.6.2

 -- Olivier Berten <olivier.berten@gmail.com>  Wed, 04 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

